<h1>Book Swap Confirmed!</h1>

<p>Hi <%= @requestee.name %>,</p>

<p>Great news! You have successfully accepted the book swap request from <strong><%= @requester.name %></strong>.</p>

<div style="margin: 20px 0; padding: 15px; background-color: #d4edda; border-left: 4px solid #28a745;">
  <h3>Swap Details:</h3>
  <p>
    <strong>You receive:</strong> <%= @listing.title %> by <%= @listing.author_name %><br/>
    <strong>You give:</strong> <%= @offered_listing.title %> by <%= @offered_listing.author_name %>
  </p>
</div>

<p>You can now coordinate the book exchange with <%= @requester.name %>. Please contact them to arrange pickup or delivery.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br/>
The Kitab Sata Pata Team</p>
